Are you ready take the last step in our journey? You have survived the hordes of nightmare creatures and the every-lasting darkness. You have gone to the forge of worlds, and are ready to let out your battle cry. The Justice League has dwlinded in numbers, and Barbatos has won...or has he?  
  
In an episode so BIG it had to be split into two parts, the guys discuss the POWER of HOPE, the metal of possibility and staying power of the Batman Who Laughs!  
  
If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
